---
title: BakeSmart - Pattern Library
---
<header aria-labelledby="welcome-message" class="page__section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="guide__section-header">
      <h1 id="welcome-message" class="header--primary">BakeSmart's Pattern Library</h1>
      <p>Welcome to BakeSmart's pattern library. A component-driven library that's core focus is to provide develpers and designers with the necessary pieces to build and maintain the evolving interface. The libary consists of four main pieces: elements, components, layout and resources. Similar to BakeSmart's interface, the pattern library is continuing to grow and evolve. To ensure you have the most update pieces, check back from time to time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
<!-- Elements -->
<section role="region" aria-label="BakeSmart Pattern Library Elements" id="elements" class="guide__section">
  <header class="guide__section-header">
    <h2>Elements</h2>
  </header>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="guide__section-content">
      <%= partial 'elements/colors' %>
    </div>
    <aside role="complementary" class="guide__section-aside">
      <nav role="navigation">
        <label>Section Nav</label>
        <ul>
          <% data.page_navigation.elements_navigation.each do |i| %>
            <li>
              <%= link_to i.title, i.url %>
            </li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- Components -->
<section role="region" aria-label="BakeSmart Pattern Library Elements" id="components" class="guide__section">
  <header class="guide__section-header">
    <h2>Components</h2>
  </header>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="guide__section-content">
      <%= partial 'components/alerts' %>
      <%= partial 'components/buttons' %>
      <%= partial 'components/cards' %>
    </div>
    <aside role="complementary" class="guide__section-aside">
      <nav role="navigation">
        <label>Section Nav</label>
        <ul>
          <% data.page_navigation.components_navigation.each do |i| %>
            <li>
              <%= link_to i.title, i.url %>
            </li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
